262
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:42,523
- I just heard it.
- Yes, Lex.

263
00:29:42,695 --> 00:29:45,061
Don't repeat what I say
when I say something.

264
00:29:45,231 --> 00:29:47,392
- I won't repeat what you say.
